      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VICTA WALLY (1) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and two placings from eight starts. Comes off a (30.79) win last time, scoring by 0.8 lengths in a Grade 5 over 530m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. ZINFANDEL EMMA (2) won again in quick time after leading them home making it five on end, scoring by 8 lengths (19.54) at this track over 342m. Yet to taste defeat from two runs out of this box. One of the leading chances again. MCCRACKEN (8) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (25.78) in a Grade 6 at Murray Bridge. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature. CLAYMORE LASS (4) bold run expected on best form.",
